  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to 400 degrees Fahrenheit",
    "Mix speculaas spice mix and Korean chili flakes in a small bowl",
    "Brush the fish balls with sesame oil and coat with the spice mix",
    "Grill the fish balls for 5 minutes per side, until cooked through",
    "Roll out the sujebi dough to a thickness of 1/8 inch",
    "Cut out small squares of dough and wrap each fish ball in a square",
    "Grill the sujebi for 2 minutes per side, until golden brown",
    "Serve the sujebi with a drizzle of lemon juice and a sprinkle of toasted sesame seeds and chopped green onions"
